u link to good examples and blog posts so I can start cooking up ideas? \u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lucia Cerchie","url":"https://dev.to/cerchie"},"datePublished":"2021-11-09T14:56:20Z","dateModified":"2021-11-09T14:56:20Z","url":"https://dev.to/cerchie/comment/1jhil","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":9}],"comment":[{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-805179","text":"\u003cp\u003eHey, I've curated this list of resources on GitHub actions, Check it out😊 \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://twitter.com/coderlens/status/1459799868386394112\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003etwitter.com/coderlens/status/14597...\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lenin (he/they)","url":"https://dev.to/coderlens"},"datePublished":"2021-11-14T15:35:15Z","dateModified":"2021-11-14T15:35:15Z","url":"https://dev.to/coderlens/comment/1jl2b","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":6}],"parentItem":{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802901"}},{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-803084","text":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"mentioned-user\" href=\"https://dev.to/cerchie\"\u003e@cerchie\u003c/a\u003e\n highly recommend you check out this blog from \u003ca class=\"mentioned-user\" href=\"https://dev.to/blackgirlbytes\"\u003e@blackgirlbytes\u003c/a\u003e\n! 😊 \u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Gracie Gregory (she/her)","url":"https://dev.to/graciegregory"},"datePublished":"2021-11-09T21:39:06Z","dateModified":"2021-11-09T21:39:06Z","url":"https://dev.to/graciegregory/comment/1jhpm","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":5}],"parentItem":{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802901"}}]},{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802793","text":"\u003cp\u003eReally excited for this Hackathon 🚀🔥\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBut where can I register for this hackathon?\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Atharva Shirdhankar","url":"https://dev.to/hey_atharva"},"datePublished":"2021-11-09T11:04:10Z","dateModified":"2021-11-09T11:04:10Z","url":"https://dev.to/hey_atharva/comment/1jheh","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":4}],"comment":[{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802903","text":"\u003cp\u003elooks like if you follow the submission rules here you should be good, but I'd definitely also wait on an offical DEV.to rep to answer as well \u003ca href=\"https://dev.to/devteam/join-us-for-the-2021-github-actions-hackathon-on-dev-4hn4#how-to-submit\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edev.to/devteam/join-us-for-the-202...\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lucia Cerchie","url":"https://dev.to/cerchie"},"datePublished":"2021-11-09T14:57:55Z","dateModified":"2021-11-09T14:57:55Z","url":"https://dev.to/cerchie/comment/1jhin","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":4}],"parentItem":{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802793"}}]},{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-814886","text":"\u003cp\u003eHey \u003ca class=\"mentioned-user\" href=\"https://dev.to/blackgirlbytes\"\u003e@blackgirlbytes\u003c/a\u003e \u0026amp; \u003ca class=\"mentioned-user\" href=\"https://dev.to/mishmanners\"\u003e@mishmanners\u003c/a\u003e ! 👋\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI'm having a GitHub related issue that is preventing me from applying to the hackathon.\u003cbr\u003e\nI've already filed a ticket (#1415845) but I don't think it'll be fixed in time for me to participate...\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe gist is that I'm trying to publish my action to the marketplace but the checkbox when drafting a new release does not appear (the \"Publish this Action to Marketplace\" banner on the repo does however).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"GeopJr","url":"https://dev.to/geopjr"},"datePublished":"2021-12-05T21:01:30Z","dateModified":"2021-12-05T21:01:30Z","url":"https://dev.to/geopjr/comment/1k9bk","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":1}],"comment":[{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-814891","text":"\u003cp\u003eHi \u003ca class=\"mentioned-user\" href=\"https://dev.to/geopjr\"\u003e@geopjr\u003c/a\u003e\n ! Apologies that you're having this issue. I will try to flag your issue to the right group. The good news is you don't have to publish your action to the marketplace to participate in the Hackathon. In the rules outlined, here's all you need to do:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDocument your project journey along the way with the #ActionsHackathon21 tag.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSubmit your project as a DEV post by filling out this template to share your workflow/s (.yml) and/or code repository.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlease make sure the project links to the appropriate GitHub Actions repository, and includes an open source license and README.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eReview these guidelines for more info: \u003ca href=\"https://dev.to/devteam/join-us-for-the-2021-github-actions-hackathon-on-dev-4hn4\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edev.to/devteam/join-us-for-the-202...\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Rizèl Scarlett","url":"https://dev.to/blackgirlbytes"},"datePublished":"2021-12-05T21:22:58Z","dateModified":"2021-12-06T13:34:16Z","url":"https://dev.to/blackgirlbytes/comment/1k9bp","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":4}],"parentItem":{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-814886"}}]},{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-816612","text":"\u003cp\u003eHello \u003ca class=\"mentioned-user\" href=\"https://dev.to/blackgirlbytes\"\u003e@blackgirlbytes\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca class=\"mentioned-user\" href=\"https://dev.to/mishmanners\"\u003e@mishmanners\u003c/a\u003e and all participants! Thank you for organizing such a stimulating event. I've learned so many things about GitHub Actions in the last few days that I can't count.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI developed a Developers' Collaborative Playlist with using GitHub Actions and documented it:\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"ltag__link\"\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"/oz9un\" class=\"ltag__link__link\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"ltag__link__pic\"\u003e\n      \u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--JqTwFl9G--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--vOGUbXRz--/c_fill%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_150%2Cq_auto%2Cw_150/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/709742/819a4005-40d3-4438-91fb-1ba2d12dc945.jpeg\" alt=\"oz9un\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"/oz9un/developers-collaborative-playlist-3eih\" class=\"ltag__link__link\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"ltag__link__content\"\u003e\n      \u003ch2\u003eDevelopers' Collaborative Playlist\u003c/h2\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003eoz9un ・ Dec 7 ・ 6 min read\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"ltag__link__taglist\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"ltag__link__tag\"\u003e#actionshackathon21\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"ltag__link__tag\"\u003e#github\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"ltag__link__tag\"\u003e#spotify\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"ltag__link__tag\"\u003e#opensource\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eI also referenced to my GitHub repository in this dev article. Is there anything else I need to do to participate 